          "date": "2012-06-08 10:10:06.000000000",
          "tz": -420
        },
        "subject": "LU-1438 quota: quota active checking is missed on slave",
        "message": "LU-1438 quota: quota active checking is missed on slave\n\nOn quota slave, we missed checking if quota is enabled in the\nquota_check_common() and several other places. Which could cause\nslave retry acquire quota in quota_chk_acq_common() infinitely\nwhen the quota is already turned off on master.\n\nSigned-off-by: Niu Yawei <niu@whamcloud.com>\nChange-Id: I707bc34684e95f2a0beec99548dc2d78a4ce8bbf\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/b1_8"
    }
  },
